org.turbogwt.mvp.databind

Class DatabindViewEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.turbogwt.mvp.databind.DatabindViewEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Binder, HasDatabindUiHandler, HasDatabindValues, WidgetBinder

    public class DatabindViewEngine
extends Object
implements WidgetBinder, HasDatabindValues, HasDatabindUiHandler
    This class should be used by any DatabindView as a delegatee. You can even create an abstract view implementing DatabindView and delegating the properly methods to this engine. Then all your views supporting databinding could extend from this one.
    Author:
    Danilo Reinert
    See Also:
    DatabindViewImpl
